blueprint.description:
Generates 2.4GW and enough fuel cells for ~650 more reactors (i.e. 9 of the 10GW layout) plus some nuclear train fuel.

Noxy's Waterfill is easiest, or bring in 24 water pipes to the back.

The reactor comes from
https://factorioprints.com/view/-M8JPYKBgXXIuHNXu-3X
with no changes other than the power default "on".

I can't find the original source for the Kovarex refinement but it's been through so many changes as I've learned its weaknesses that it's mostly my own, now.
blueprint.label: Kovarex/Nuc (2.4GW)
